Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My only wish is to become\Nthe strongest man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you grant me\Nwhat I desire, o demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO] "I could, although\Nit would come at the cost
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of your life."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no matter. Living a long\Nlife was never my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO] "However, though\NI can give this power to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot simply\Nconjure it into being."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"If I am to grant you strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it must be taken from one\Nwho bears your blood."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work.\NI haven't got any living kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[murmurs]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He says you need\Nbut sire a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon! Seal the pact\Nand grant me my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:00:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIANT MONSTER 8A groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[thudding]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE] You are the strongest\Nwoman in the world, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Bosse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What about?\NDid you come here for a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- [BOSSE] No.\N- [SHIINA] Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to marry me\Nand bear me a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You speak nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I live only in pursuit\Nof strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE] My dream is to become\Nthe strongest man in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will not rest until\NI've made it come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHIINA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE]\NSo be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHIINA, BOSSE panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as a man should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]\NStraightforward, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs] Why did I feel so\Ncompelled to become stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that the men around\Nsimply weren't strong enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHIINA]\NHmm? No, it wasn't that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. Right. Pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHIINA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE, SHIINA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[OGRE 8A growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My child... is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[bellows]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[OGRES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGER 8A]\NShe just gave birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been spilling\Nblood, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you were out ending\Nlives, a new one was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHIINA]\NLook; he's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But a rather small one for the\Nchild of two giants, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[MIRANJO]\N"If I am to grant you strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it must be taken from one\Nwho bears your blood."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHIINA]\NHmm. Even so, he's very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI babbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE huffing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE snarls]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGERS gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This place will mark\Nthe end of my long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me! I will make this land\Nthe seat of my kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGERS cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE] My son... shall live\Na life unconstrained by want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make that my only goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NKing Bosse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wish to know who is the\Nstrongest person in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as of this moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying it isn't me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NYou must recite the incantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror, Mirror, hear my call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the strongest\Nof them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] This person\Nis the strongest alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] So, then,\Nare you feeling reassured?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,An interesting turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] King Bosse... The\Ntime has come to kill Hiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you give your blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As promised, so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Bojji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I had orders and\NI couldn't defy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please, wait.\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what\NI have to say first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When I chose to let you live,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I forfeited my place\Nat the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I return,\Nmy life could be at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not ready to give it up\Nyet, so I won't be going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls] I can't believe\Nwhat a coward you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hokuro, what do you expect\Nthem to do when you return?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter.\NIt's my duty to report this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your report would find\Nits way to the person
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,who gave the order.\NThe king himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Hiling knows\Nnothing of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and King Daida\Nis her own beloved child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What will she do when you tell\Nher he had his brother killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave out your\Nexplanations and only tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,what I saw for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly, I've done neither of us\Nany favors by leaving you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NSpare me your pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]\NStop trying to play the hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You did leave me alive,\Nwhich means I'm obliged
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to return to the castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...and inform the queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she loved Prince Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And if his soul can't\Nseek comfort from those
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who loved him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...after everything\Nhe went through...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...then all his suffering\Nwas for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- [HOKURO groans]\N- [DOMAS] Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! You're a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and die the finest\Ndeath you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO snarls]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NLimb from limb...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be torn...\Nlimb from limb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[MONSTER 8A growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,These monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You plan to turn them\Nagainst Hiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NIndeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward, Apeas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[MONSTER 8B growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS]\NThe first one was drawing me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[MONSTER 8B growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[APEAS]\NI got sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand down, Apeas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR]\NKing Bosse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[MONSTERS growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[MONSTERS growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NForgive me, Miranjo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My blood hasn't raced\Nlike that in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your plan to assassinate Hiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- [MAGIC MIRROR] Yes?\N- I approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] Dorshe is the only\None who poses a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] How did I trick myself\Ninto coming back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But you did leave me alive,\Nwhich means I'm obliged
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to return to the castle\Nand inform the queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride just weighs you down\Nin the end, eh, Hokuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 8A]\NReady!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NPrince Bojji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- [SOLDIERS yelling]\N- [SOLDIER 8A] What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Hiling.\NDo not leave my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting, yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- [DOMAS] Hokuro!\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.42,0:12:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[DORSHE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIERS gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS snarls]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Daida?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NKing Daida?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[DORSHE]\NHe parried! That technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Domas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- [SOLDIER 8A] Wait. Is that...?\N- [SOLDIER 8B] Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- [SOLDIER 8C] It's him!\N- [SOLDIER 8D] Master Domas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]\NHokuro. Apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, you came...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Dorshe!\NI want Domas's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, take his head! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji is safe!\NHe is not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:14:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 8D]\NBut then, what's happening...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NMirror, Mirror, hear my call.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the strongest\Nof them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] This person\Nis the strongest alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[hissing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunting, groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[hissing, growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOSSE]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bebin, from this day forward,\Nyou shall serve with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the royal elite forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect great things...\Nsnake charmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Heh.\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not in my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have given me far more\Nthan could ever be repaid
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,through a gesture such\Nas this, Master Bebin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN]\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[SOLDIER 8F]\NWhat is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji's journeyed to the\Nunderworld for his training!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He grows stronger\Nas we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- [HILING sighs]\N- [DORSHE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really... still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NHe is, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,\Nyour life is spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You are hereby relieved\Nof duty and banished
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,from the castle\Nwith these words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[inaudible]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NNow begone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS grunts]\NYes, sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving now, Hokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO grunts]\NSir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NMaster Domas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true? Could Prince\NBojji really still be alive
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,like King Daida was saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NIt could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't follow him into the pit\Nto confirm he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Bebin's\Nnetwork informed the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure... the prince\Nmust have made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NRight. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Master Domas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS sniffles]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not King Daida,\Nbut King Bosse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NI don't fully understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but King Bosse has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives on within\Nthe body of Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NImpossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But where is King Daida, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] I couldn't even\Nbegin to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NSir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] I need to find a way\Nto use my right arm again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... I'll teach\Nyou swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] Where we're going,\Nyou'll need it to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will we be going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] Deep beneath the castle,\Nto a gateway that opens
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,into the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NThe underworld...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS] A fell place that draws\Nmonsters to it like a beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to close it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wait until now\Nto deal with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only told to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be more to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO] I can't forgive\Nwhat you did to Prince Bojji,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and I doubt I ever will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if I'd been there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that I\Ncouldn't have saved him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...because I'm too soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I have\Nto become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward\Nto learning from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS]\NYou've helped me recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,something, too, Hokuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I had forgotten just how\Nvaluable innocence can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I could\Nhardly bear to face him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No--that's not\Nimportant right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on nothing\Nbut the task at hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO]\NRight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOMAS bellows]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[HOKURO bellows]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NDid itty bitty Bojji actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] No way. Bojji couldn't\Neven budge a hammer like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,let alone swing it.\NBut what is he using?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- [DESPA] Kage.\N- [KAGE] Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sneak up on me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Bojji's here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NMm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The long-awaited day\Nhas finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji has fully\Nmastered the Despa arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\N"Fully mastered"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[HILING]\NKing Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you... changed, somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You still can't tell who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorshe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[DORSHE]\NSire?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[DORSHE groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[DORSHE grunts]\NWait. What did you just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] As I would expect\Nfrom the Big Four's strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[inaudible]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAGIC MIRROR] Apeas, do you\Nhave any idea what King Bosse
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,might be whispering to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A good question.\NI can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- [DAIDA] Hiling.\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be fooled. Your eyes\Ntell you I am your son, Daida,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but in truth, I am Bosse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror! Where are you, Mirror?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NIn the chamber...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...Apeas knocked me out\Nwith a surprise blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they toss me\Ninto a cell somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[DAIDA]\NSomething is strange here.
